                    <div class="solution-description">
                        Let’s solve the vacant church problem.
                        <br><br>
                        We created the McMass project because we want to see our churches continue to thrive in modern culture. By building a McDonalds, a church not only gains valuable supplementary income that can be put towards outreach programs,development, and charity, but also situates itself within the very day life of the community. 
                        <br><br>
                        Think of the opportunities this presents: to be able to reach people everyday, outside of formal worship. The McMass project is the chance to establish the real-world equivalent of social media presence.
                    </div>
